commitResults.messageTitle: Add support for parsing Bookmark command

commitResults.messageBody:
A new boolean field isBookmark has been added to Company.
Calling Bookmark on a company with the valid index will toggle
the isBookmark value for the company.

Add new test cases to ensure that BookmarkCommand works correctly
as intended.

A new RemoveBookmarkCommand has been added to
remove bookmarked companies.

A new field Bookmark has been added to Company instead of
the previous boolean field. This is done to keep in line with
how the other fields of Company works.

A new class TypicalBookmarkedCompanies which simulates a list
of bookmarked companies has been added to facilitate testing of
BookmarkCommand. Test cases for BookmarkCommand has also been
updated.

There was a bug where RemoveBookmarkCommandParser was giving
the wrong MESSAGE_USAGE. This was fixed with the correct one and
test cases have been implemented for RemoveBookmarkCommandParser.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add functionality for showing bookmarked company
commitResults.messageBody:
A BookmarkListCommand class has been added to support the
feature of showing all bookmarked companies.

commitResults.messageTitle: Show bookmark value in command message

commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, bookmarking or removing a bookmarked company
will cause the app to go back to the default list. This
has been changed so that the last shown list remains.
